description: Nestled in the heart of South Boston, 10 G St offers an incredible opportunity to restore a classic home to its full potential. Just minutes from downtown, this prime location provides unbeatable city access, while the private roof deck showcases stunning skyline views. Inside, the spacious layout is brimming with character, featuring fire-placed bedrooms that exude warmth and charm. High ceilings, large windows, and original details offer the perfect canvas for customization. With thoughtful updates, this home can seamlessly blend historic elegance with modern luxury. The vibrant neighborhood offers trendy restaurants, shops, and waterfront access, making it a sought-after destination. Whether you're an investor or a homeowner eager to craft your dream space, 10 G St is a rare find in an unbeatable location. Don't miss this chance to create something truly special! Sellers prefer to sell 8 G St and 10 G St as a package but are willing to sell separately.
